thread.title: CSX Corp to reduce train operations in Erwin, Tennessee
thread.title_full: CSX Corp to reduce train operations in Erwin, Tennessee | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: CSX Corp to reduce train operations in Erwin, Tennessee
text:
Oct 15 U.S. railroad CSX Corp said it would reduce train operations in Erwin, Tennessee due to lower coal traffic in the region.
The company said it would also close a locomotive service center, project shop and car shop in the town, affecting 300 employees. (Reporting by Ankit Ajmera in Bengaluru; Editing by Anil D'Silva)
